WEBVTT

00:00:01.650 --> 00:00:06.550
Bismillah irrahman irrahim

00:00:06.550 --> 00:00:13.590
In the name of Allah, the most gracious, the most merciful.

00:00:13.590 --> 00:00:19.760
Subhanallah wa rahmanillah wa la ilaha illallah

00:00:19.760 --> 00:00:21.760
Par excellence presents

00:00:21.760 --> 00:00:24.760
wa la ilaha illallah

00:00:24.760 --> 00:00:32.590
Lessons from the stories of the prophets

00:00:32.590 --> 00:00:45.950
by Mufti Ismail ibn Musa Menk

00:00:45.950 --> 00:00:49.950
Adam, alayhi salam, on earth, part 2

00:00:50.350 --> 00:00:54.850
Adam, peace be upon him, on earth, part 2

00:00:54.850 --> 00:00:57.850
Assalamu alaykum wa rahmatullahi wa barakatuh

00:00:57.850 --> 00:01:01.610
Bismillah irrahman irrahim

00:01:01.610 --> 00:01:03.610
Alhamdulillahi rabbil alameen

00:01:03.610 --> 00:01:05.610
wa s-salatu wa s-salamu ala al-mab'uth

00:01:05.610 --> 00:01:07.610
Rahmatan lil alameen

00:01:07.610 --> 00:01:10.610
Nabi'ina Muhammadin wa ala alihi wa ashabihi ajma'ina wa ba'd

00:01:10.610 --> 00:01:13.610
All praise is due to Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:01:13.610 --> 00:01:16.610
Blessings and salutations upon Muhammad salallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:01:16.610 --> 00:01:18.610
We ask Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:01:18.610 --> 00:01:20.610
to bless him and all his companions

00:01:20.610 --> 00:01:22.610
to bless every single one of us

00:01:22.610 --> 00:01:24.610
to bless our offspring those to come up to the day of Qiyamah

00:01:24.610 --> 00:01:26.610
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:01:26.610 --> 00:01:28.610
keep them all steadfast on this deen

00:01:28.610 --> 00:01:30.610
and may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:01:30.610 --> 00:01:32.610
keep us as well steadfast on the deen

00:01:32.610 --> 00:01:34.610
This evening as we were

00:01:34.610 --> 00:01:36.610
reading the Salah, the Taraweeh

00:01:36.610 --> 00:01:40.370
a thought came to my mind

00:01:40.370 --> 00:01:44.370
and that is a hadith of the prophet salallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:01:44.370 --> 00:01:47.370
narrated by Aisha radiallahu anha

00:01:47.370 --> 00:01:51.370
she says that she used to watch the prophet salallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:01:51.370 --> 00:01:53.370
read Salah at night

00:01:53.370 --> 00:01:55.370
so often

00:01:55.370 --> 00:01:57.370
most of the night, almost all of the night

00:01:57.370 --> 00:02:02.370
to the degree that his feet became swollen

00:02:02.370 --> 00:02:05.370
and she asked him a question

00:02:05.370 --> 00:02:07.370
she says, oh messenger of Allah

00:02:07.370 --> 00:02:09.370
salallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:02:09.370 --> 00:02:13.370
Allah has kept you free from sin

00:02:13.370 --> 00:02:15.370
and Allah has forgiven you

00:02:15.370 --> 00:02:17.370
in fact, anything to come

00:02:17.370 --> 00:02:19.370
and anything that was, there is nothing

00:02:19.370 --> 00:02:21.370
you have such a high rank

00:02:21.370 --> 00:02:24.370
you are so high, you know your rank

00:02:24.370 --> 00:02:27.370
so why is it that you are spending so much time

00:02:27.370 --> 00:02:32.370
in Salah that your feet are actually swollen

00:02:32.370 --> 00:02:35.370
and he answered so beautifully

00:02:35.370 --> 00:02:37.370
and I think we should all be thinking of it

00:02:37.370 --> 00:02:40.370
because none of our feet are swollen right now

00:02:40.370 --> 00:02:42.370
yet we find it so difficult to stand

00:02:42.370 --> 00:02:43.370
for one hour sometimes

00:02:43.370 --> 00:02:45.370
may Allah make it easy for us

00:02:45.370 --> 00:02:47.370
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:02:47.370 --> 00:02:50.370
grant us a lesson from the answer

00:02:50.370 --> 00:02:53.370
of this most beloved creature of Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:02:53.370 --> 00:02:54.370
he says

00:02:58.370 --> 00:03:00.370
should I not be a slave

00:03:00.370 --> 00:03:03.370
who is grateful, who is thankful

00:03:03.370 --> 00:03:05.370
to his creator

00:03:05.370 --> 00:03:07.370
for the status that he was granted

00:03:07.370 --> 00:03:09.370
subhanallah

00:03:09.370 --> 00:03:11.370
so with him, he had the status

00:03:11.370 --> 00:03:12.370
he knew it

00:03:12.370 --> 00:03:14.370
he had this link with Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:03:14.370 --> 00:03:16.370
and he wanted to please Allah even more

00:03:16.370 --> 00:03:18.370
so that's what made him happy

00:03:18.370 --> 00:03:20.370
it made him happy when he could stand

00:03:20.370 --> 00:03:22.370
and his legs were swollen

00:03:22.370 --> 00:03:25.370
because of standing for his own creator

00:03:25.370 --> 00:03:27.370
I want to ask a question

00:03:27.370 --> 00:03:28.370
and a serious question

00:03:28.370 --> 00:03:30.370
what makes us happy

00:03:30.370 --> 00:03:32.370
let's be frank, let's be honest

00:03:32.370 --> 00:03:34.370
if you struck a good deal

00:03:34.370 --> 00:03:36.370
and today business was brisk

00:03:36.370 --> 00:03:37.370
we become happy

00:03:37.370 --> 00:03:39.370
if we are feeling healthy

00:03:39.370 --> 00:03:40.370
and our sickness is gone

00:03:40.370 --> 00:03:41.370
we become happy

00:03:41.370 --> 00:03:43.370
if we have just purchased clothing

00:03:43.370 --> 00:03:44.370
that fits us nicely

00:03:44.370 --> 00:03:45.370
and it looks good

00:03:45.370 --> 00:03:47.370
we become excited

00:03:47.370 --> 00:03:49.370
this is what makes us happy

00:03:49.370 --> 00:03:51.370
if for example we've purchased a new vehicle

00:03:51.370 --> 00:03:53.370
and it's sitting there in the front

00:03:53.370 --> 00:03:54.370
we're happy

00:03:54.370 --> 00:03:55.370
masha'Allah

00:03:55.370 --> 00:03:57.370
if for example we've won a ticket

00:03:57.370 --> 00:03:59.370
to Hawaii or Honolulu

00:03:59.370 --> 00:04:00.370
for a holiday

00:04:00.370 --> 00:04:02.370
we're excited, we're happy

00:04:02.370 --> 00:04:03.370
let's be honest

00:04:03.370 --> 00:04:05.370
this is what makes us happy

00:04:05.370 --> 00:04:07.370
if our salaries have increased

00:04:07.370 --> 00:04:09.370
and our hours have decreased

00:04:09.370 --> 00:04:10.370
we become happy

00:04:10.370 --> 00:04:12.370
yes

00:04:12.370 --> 00:04:14.370
now let's take a look at the lesson

00:04:14.370 --> 00:04:15.370
that we have

00:04:15.370 --> 00:04:17.370
from this blessed hadith of the Prophet

00:04:17.370 --> 00:04:19.370
صلى الله عليه وسلم

00:04:19.370 --> 00:04:22.370
yes, it is natural to be happy

00:04:22.370 --> 00:04:23.370
at what I've just mentioned

00:04:23.370 --> 00:04:25.370
but that happiness is momentary

00:04:25.370 --> 00:04:27.370
it is just for a moment

00:04:27.370 --> 00:04:29.370
it is not supposed to be prolonged happiness

00:04:29.370 --> 00:04:31.370
the true excitement must be

00:04:31.370 --> 00:04:32.370
when your legs start paining

00:04:32.370 --> 00:04:33.370
and you're standing

00:04:33.370 --> 00:04:34.370
and you say

00:04:34.370 --> 00:04:35.370
Ya Allah, this is for you

00:04:35.370 --> 00:04:36.370
Allahu Akbar

00:04:36.370 --> 00:04:38.370
Ya Allah, if it was not for you

00:04:38.370 --> 00:04:40.370
I would not even have dressed appropriately

00:04:40.370 --> 00:04:41.370
Allahu Akbar

00:04:41.370 --> 00:04:43.370
so when you are dressed appropriately

00:04:43.370 --> 00:04:44.370
covering properly

00:04:44.370 --> 00:04:46.370
and people are laughing at you

00:04:46.370 --> 00:04:47.370
and calling you names

00:04:47.370 --> 00:04:48.370
you need to say

00:04:48.370 --> 00:04:50.370
Ya Allah, this is what makes me so happy

00:04:50.370 --> 00:04:51.370
because I know you're writing

00:04:51.370 --> 00:04:52.370
next to my name

00:04:52.370 --> 00:04:54.370
rewards that will grant me

00:04:54.370 --> 00:04:55.370
entry into Jannah

00:04:55.370 --> 00:04:56.370
and Allah says

00:05:04.370 --> 00:05:05.370
the criminals used to laugh

00:05:05.370 --> 00:05:06.370
at the believers

00:05:06.370 --> 00:05:07.370
in this world

00:05:07.370 --> 00:05:08.370
the criminals used to laugh

00:05:08.370 --> 00:05:09.370
at the believers

00:05:09.370 --> 00:05:12.370
if you're dressed as a Muslim woman

00:05:12.370 --> 00:05:13.370
one of the ways of telling

00:05:13.370 --> 00:05:15.370
that you are dressed properly

00:05:15.370 --> 00:05:16.370
is sometime in your life

00:05:16.370 --> 00:05:18.370
someone will pass a negative comment

00:05:18.370 --> 00:05:20.370
or someone will laugh at you

00:05:20.370 --> 00:05:22.370
or someone will say something discouraging

00:05:22.370 --> 00:05:24.370
then you know you've dressed properly

00:05:24.370 --> 00:05:25.370
Subhanallah

00:05:25.370 --> 00:05:28.370
because that's Allah's plan

00:05:28.370 --> 00:05:29.370
and I'm talking here

00:05:29.370 --> 00:05:30.370
of when you were living

00:05:30.370 --> 00:05:32.370
in a non-Muslim country

00:05:32.370 --> 00:05:33.370
and sometimes even from amongst

00:05:33.370 --> 00:05:35.370
our own family members

00:05:35.370 --> 00:05:36.370
they discourage us

00:05:36.370 --> 00:05:37.370
no, you're too young

00:05:37.370 --> 00:05:38.370
to cover your hair

00:05:38.370 --> 00:05:39.370
don't cover it now

00:05:39.370 --> 00:05:40.370
wait until you grow

00:05:40.370 --> 00:05:41.370
how are you going to get married

00:05:41.370 --> 00:05:42.370
they're not going to see

00:05:42.370 --> 00:05:43.370
what the head and shoulders

00:05:43.370 --> 00:05:44.370
look like in your hair

00:05:44.370 --> 00:05:45.370
Allahu Akbar

00:05:45.370 --> 00:05:47.370
may Allah safeguard us

00:05:47.370 --> 00:05:48.370
this is the mentality

00:05:48.370 --> 00:05:49.370
that people have

00:05:49.370 --> 00:05:50.370
yet we don't understand

00:05:50.370 --> 00:05:51.370
when we cover it

00:05:51.370 --> 00:05:52.370
for the sake of Allah

00:05:52.370 --> 00:05:53.370
it must make us happy

00:05:53.370 --> 00:05:54.370
imagine

00:05:54.370 --> 00:05:55.370
on one hand

00:05:55.370 --> 00:05:56.370
we got the example

00:05:56.370 --> 00:05:57.370
of the swollen legs

00:05:57.370 --> 00:05:58.370
what is that example

00:05:58.370 --> 00:06:00.370
compared to just covering properly

00:06:00.370 --> 00:06:01.370
Allahu Akbar

00:06:01.370 --> 00:06:04.370
may Allah use us really

00:06:04.370 --> 00:06:06.370
in His cause

00:06:06.370 --> 00:06:07.370
and may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:06:07.370 --> 00:06:09.370
accept us this evening

00:06:09.370 --> 00:06:10.370
to make a resolution

00:06:10.370 --> 00:06:11.370
that we will dress appropriately

00:06:11.370 --> 00:06:13.370
come what may

00:06:13.370 --> 00:06:15.370
and may Allah make us from those

00:06:15.370 --> 00:06:16.370
who can make a resolution

00:06:16.370 --> 00:06:17.370
this evening

00:06:17.370 --> 00:06:18.370
that come what may

00:06:18.370 --> 00:06:20.370
we will fulfill our five salah

00:06:20.370 --> 00:06:22.370
for the sake of Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:06:22.370 --> 00:06:24.370
it is not worth leaving it out

00:06:24.370 --> 00:06:25.370
I was thinking moments ago

00:06:25.370 --> 00:06:26.370
as I was getting up

00:06:26.370 --> 00:06:27.370
that for myself

00:06:27.370 --> 00:06:30.370
it has rekindled the link

00:06:30.370 --> 00:06:31.370
with Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:06:31.370 --> 00:06:32.370
to make mention of

00:06:32.370 --> 00:06:33.370
how everything began

00:06:33.370 --> 00:06:34.370
and the creation of Adam

00:06:34.370 --> 00:06:35.370
alayhi salam

00:06:35.370 --> 00:06:37.370
and the stories of the prophets

00:06:37.370 --> 00:06:38.370
not to say there was no link

00:06:38.370 --> 00:06:39.370
but we rekindled

00:06:39.370 --> 00:06:40.370
the link

00:06:40.370 --> 00:06:43.370
and we want to keep that fire going

00:06:43.370 --> 00:06:46.370
we want to keep that light going

00:06:46.370 --> 00:06:47.370
I wonder if it is the same

00:06:47.370 --> 00:06:48.370
for all of us

00:06:48.370 --> 00:06:49.370
that we have this link

00:06:49.370 --> 00:06:50.370
we feel that really

00:06:50.370 --> 00:06:51.370
we are going to return

00:06:51.370 --> 00:06:52.370
to Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:06:52.370 --> 00:06:53.370
this evening inshallah

00:06:53.370 --> 00:06:55.370
we will be completing

00:06:55.370 --> 00:06:56.370
the story of Adam

00:06:56.370 --> 00:06:57.370
alayhi salatu wa salam

00:06:57.370 --> 00:06:59.370
with a few details inshallah

00:06:59.370 --> 00:07:00.370
and thereafter

00:07:00.370 --> 00:07:01.370
we will continue tomorrow

00:07:01.370 --> 00:07:03.370
with the stories of

00:07:03.370 --> 00:07:04.370
the other prophets

00:07:04.370 --> 00:07:06.370
of Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:07:06.370 --> 00:07:07.370
to start with

00:07:07.370 --> 00:07:08.370
this Quran

00:07:08.370 --> 00:07:09.370
we need to understand

00:07:09.370 --> 00:07:11.370
as I had made mention of

00:07:11.370 --> 00:07:13.370
at the end of yesterday's talk

00:07:13.370 --> 00:07:15.370
that Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala says

00:07:15.370 --> 00:07:18.370
we will send for you reminders

00:07:18.370 --> 00:07:19.370
and whosoever turns away

00:07:19.370 --> 00:07:20.370
from the reminders

00:07:20.370 --> 00:07:22.370
they will be resurrected blind

00:07:22.370 --> 00:07:23.370
if you recall

00:07:23.370 --> 00:07:24.370
we made mention of it

00:07:24.370 --> 00:07:25.370
and we read the verse

00:07:25.370 --> 00:07:27.370
which happens to be in surah Taha

00:07:27.370 --> 00:07:28.370
and thereafter

00:07:28.370 --> 00:07:29.370
there is a point

00:07:29.370 --> 00:07:32.370
that needs to be highlighted

00:07:32.370 --> 00:07:35.370
what did the kuffar of Quraish

00:07:35.370 --> 00:07:36.370
used to say at the time

00:07:36.370 --> 00:07:37.370
of the prophet

00:07:37.370 --> 00:07:38.370
salallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:07:38.370 --> 00:07:40.370
when the Quran was being revealed

00:07:40.370 --> 00:07:42.370
they knew that anybody

00:07:42.370 --> 00:07:43.370
who listens to this Quran

00:07:43.370 --> 00:07:46.370
they are automatically inclined

00:07:46.370 --> 00:07:47.370
towards it

00:07:47.370 --> 00:07:48.370
one is to look at the face

00:07:48.370 --> 00:07:50.370
of Muhammad salallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:07:50.370 --> 00:07:52.370
is already a turning point

00:07:52.370 --> 00:07:53.370
you need a little bit of sincerity

00:07:53.370 --> 00:07:55.370
and you are turned

00:07:55.370 --> 00:07:56.370
and after that

00:07:56.370 --> 00:07:58.370
to listen to the words of the Quran

00:07:58.370 --> 00:07:59.370
it melts you

00:07:59.370 --> 00:08:00.370
Allahu Akbar

00:08:00.370 --> 00:08:02.370
today there were so many verses

00:08:02.370 --> 00:08:03.370
that were read

00:08:03.370 --> 00:08:04.370
and I was thinking to myself

00:08:04.370 --> 00:08:05.370
I wish I could pause

00:08:05.370 --> 00:08:06.370
to translate some of those verses

00:08:06.370 --> 00:08:07.370
one of them

00:08:07.370 --> 00:08:09.370
Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala says

00:08:19.370 --> 00:08:20.370
O man, if Allah wills

00:08:20.370 --> 00:08:21.370
He can delete you

00:08:21.370 --> 00:08:23.370
and replace you with others

00:08:23.370 --> 00:08:24.370
if Allah wants

00:08:24.370 --> 00:08:26.370
He can wipe you out

00:08:26.370 --> 00:08:27.370
and bring others

00:08:27.370 --> 00:08:28.370
in another place in the Quran

00:08:28.370 --> 00:08:29.370
Allah says the same thing

00:08:29.370 --> 00:08:31.370
that if you are not going to worship Allah

00:08:31.370 --> 00:08:33.370
if you want to turn away

00:08:33.370 --> 00:08:34.370
from Allah's worship

00:08:34.370 --> 00:08:36.370
He does not need you O man

00:08:36.370 --> 00:08:38.370
He can actually delete you

00:08:38.370 --> 00:08:39.370
you know how powerful

00:08:39.370 --> 00:08:40.370
is that word delete

00:08:40.370 --> 00:08:42.370
imagine if someone had to tell you

00:08:42.370 --> 00:08:43.370
I'm going to delete you

00:08:43.370 --> 00:08:45.370
and you look at them and say what

00:08:45.370 --> 00:08:47.370
you probably take your gun out

00:08:47.370 --> 00:08:48.370
for them in this country

00:08:48.370 --> 00:08:49.370
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:08:49.370 --> 00:08:50.370
safeguard us

00:08:50.370 --> 00:08:52.370
and here Allah is saying

00:08:52.370 --> 00:08:54.370
He's explaining how independent

00:08:54.370 --> 00:08:56.370
He is and how dependent

00:08:56.370 --> 00:08:57.370
we are

00:08:57.370 --> 00:08:58.370
He says

00:08:58.370 --> 00:09:00.370
if I so will

00:09:00.370 --> 00:09:01.370
I can actually delete you

00:09:01.370 --> 00:09:03.370
and I can bring others

00:09:03.370 --> 00:09:05.370
may Allah never do that to us

00:09:05.370 --> 00:09:07.370
so that's a powerful verse

00:09:07.370 --> 00:09:09.370
another verse that we mentioned this evening

00:09:09.370 --> 00:09:10.370
that sometimes

00:09:10.370 --> 00:09:12.370
in order to please people

00:09:12.370 --> 00:09:14.370
and to seek status

00:09:14.370 --> 00:09:15.370
we please people

00:09:15.370 --> 00:09:17.370
in the displeasure of Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:09:17.370 --> 00:09:19.370
and Allah says

00:09:22.370 --> 00:09:23.370
do they want to seek

00:09:23.370 --> 00:09:25.370
that status

00:09:25.370 --> 00:09:26.370
with those people there

00:09:26.370 --> 00:09:28.370
in the displeasure of Allah

00:09:28.370 --> 00:09:29.370
let them know

00:09:34.370 --> 00:09:35.370
it is Allah alone

00:09:35.370 --> 00:09:37.370
who owns the dignity

00:09:37.370 --> 00:09:38.370
and the status

00:09:38.370 --> 00:09:39.370
if Allah wants

00:09:39.370 --> 00:09:40.370
He can raise you

00:09:40.370 --> 00:09:41.370
and if He wants

00:09:41.370 --> 00:09:42.370
He can drop you

00:09:42.370 --> 00:09:43.370
there is no point

00:09:43.370 --> 00:09:44.370
in pleasing people

00:09:44.370 --> 00:09:45.370
in the displeasure of Allah

00:09:45.370 --> 00:09:46.370
subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:09:46.370 --> 00:09:47.370
rather

00:09:47.370 --> 00:09:48.370
if the people are displeased

00:09:48.370 --> 00:09:50.370
while Allah is pleased

00:09:50.370 --> 00:09:51.370
then Alhamdulillah

00:09:51.370 --> 00:09:53.370
we are heading in the right direction

00:09:53.370 --> 00:09:55.370
so the Quran

00:09:55.370 --> 00:09:56.370
I'd like to make mention

00:09:56.370 --> 00:09:57.370
of a very interesting story

00:09:57.370 --> 00:09:58.370
at the time of Rasulullah

00:09:58.370 --> 00:10:00.370
salallahu alayhi wasallam

00:10:00.370 --> 00:10:02.370
the kuffar of Quraysh

00:10:02.370 --> 00:10:03.370
sent one of the most eloquent

00:10:03.370 --> 00:10:04.370
from among them

